# Mercur (my-marketplace)

Commerce backend is **Mercur** on Medusa v2 — separate from Supabase. Work from `my-marketplace/` unless noted.

## Before non-trivial Mercur changes

1. Read `my-marketplace/CLAUDE.md` (task router + verification)
2. Load **`.claude/skills/mercur/SKILL.md`** (or `/mercur`) and the matching `references/*.md` topic
3. Search registry before building: `npx @mercurjs/cli@latest search --query <keyword>`
4. Prefer **MCP** for live docs; use local **llms** when MCP is unavailable

## MCP (live documentation)

Project + user Cursor config: `mercur` → `https://docs.mercurjs.com/mcp`

Tools: `search_mercur_js_documentation`, `query_docs_filesystem_mercur_js_documentation`

## llms.txt (offline)

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `my-marketplace/docs/mercur/llms.txt` | Doc index (~5KB) |
| `my-marketplace/docs/mercur/llms-full.txt` | Full docs dump (~160KB) |

Refresh: `bash my-marketplace/scripts/fetch-mercur-docs.sh`

## Hub skill topics

| Reference | Use when |
|-----------|----------|
| `references/cli.md` | create, init, search, view, add, diff |
| `references/blocks.md` | install or update registry blocks |
| `references/dashboard-page-ui.md` | admin/vendor custom pages (`src/routes`) |
| `references/dashboard-form-ui.md` | dashboard forms |
| `references/dashboard-tab-ui.md` | tabs / wizards |
| `references/medusa-ui-conformance.md` | reusable UI, `@medusajs/ui` |
| `references/migration.md` | Mercur 1.x → 2.0 |

Path: `.claude/skills/mercur/` · Cursor mirror: `.cursor/skills/mercur/`

## Secrets & dev

- Infisical: `/mercur/api` (API), `/mercur` (shared)
- API: `infisical run --path=/mercur/api -- sh -c 'cd my-marketplace/packages/api && yarn dev'`
- Docker: `mercur-postgres`, `mercur-redis` on host

## Do not confuse

- **Supabase** (`supabase/`) — iPix platform, auth, brand intelligence
- **Mercur** (`my-marketplace/`) — catalog, sellers, checkout, Stripe
